      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i just sit in these cafes here and look at everyone passing by and it hits me how much of a ghost i am. i've been in this city for a year and if i just stopped showing up tomorrow, i don't think a single person would even notice. it's like i'm just taking up space that doesn't even belong to me.",
