      "content": "but that sounds so exhausting. like, constantly trying to \"make a mark\" when you feel like you're basically invisible. honestly, the idea of just... not having to try anymore, of just fading out quietly without the drama of actually leaving a void... it feels more like peace than anything else. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise.",
